OL,7,FIn the letter the families said: "His
OL,8,Fcontinuing violence in prison,
OL,9,Fattacking prison officers in Belmarsh
OL,10,Fand now attempting to murder three
OL,11,Fmore, shows he feels no remorse and
OL,12,Fhas no respect for human life.
OL,14,F"Hashem Abedi cannot be allowed to
OL,15,Fhurt anyone else.
OL,17,F"As broken families, we firmly believe
OL,18,Fthe appropriate punishment for this
OL,19,Findividual should be solitary
OL,20,Fconfinement. In truth anything harsher
OL,21,Fwould be more fitting."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
