OL,7,F"I was absolutely shocked because we
OL,8,Fwere told he was basically in solitary
OL,9,Fconfinement," Charlotte Hodgeson said.
OL,11,F"He wasn't mixing with people, he
OL,12,Fcertainly wasn't in a kitchen.
OL,14,F"How is he allowed to do this? How is
OL,15,Fhe allowed to lead a pretty normal
OL,16,Flife? We don't."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Sir Keir Starmer says he is
OL,19,F"appalled" by the attack and promised
OL,20,Fthat the government will urgently
OL,21,Finvestigate what happened.
