OL,7,FThe Prime Minister's spokesman said:
OL,8,F"The Prime Minister is appalled by the
OL,9,Fattack that we saw at the weekend and
OL,10,Fhis thoughts are with the officers
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"Prison staff work around the clock to
OL,14,Fkeep the country safe and we will
OL,15,Fnever tolerate the violence that is
OL,16,Ftargeted towards them.
