OL,7,F"It's clear that something went
OL,8,Fterribly wrong in the management of
OL,9,Fthis offender and the Government is
OL,10,Fcommitted to carrying out an
OL,11,Finvestigation to urgently get answers."
OL,13,FHe went on: "Offenders should be
OL,14,Fmanaged in such a way that our prison
OL,15,Fofficers are kept safe and there will
OL,16,Fbe an investigation here into what
OL,17,Fhappened that allowed this incident to
OL,18,Fhappen."
