OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice said they have launched an
OL,9,Ffull independent review into the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FIn a statement, they said: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts remain with the victims of
OL,14,Fthe Manchester Arena bombing and their
OL,15,Ffamilies who are understandably
OL,16,Fconcerned by the shocking attack at
OL,17,FHMP Frankland this weekend.
